    "title": "京东规则动态一览（2025年3月17日-2025年3月21日）",
    "followRuleId": "1219095544761290752",
    "content": "<p style=\"text-align: left; line-height: 200%; background: white; margin: 0cm; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black; border: 1pt none windowtext; padding: 0cm; font-size: 12pt;\">各位商家：</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left; line-height: 200%; background: white; margin: 0cm; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\"><strong><span style=\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black; border: none windowtext 1.0pt; padding: 0cm;\">本周共公示10条规则，生效13条规则。</span></strong></span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left; line-height: 200%; background: white; margin: 0cm; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black; border: 1pt none windowtext; padding: 0cm; font-size: 12pt;\">具体内容如下，可点击查阅：</span></p>\n<p style=\"line-height: 200%; margin-right: 0cm; margin-left: 0cm; font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16.0pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">【规则公示】</span></p>\n<p style=\"line-height: 200%; margin-right: 0cm; margin-left: 0cm; font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\"><span style=\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: #4472c4;\">1</span><span style=\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: #4472c4;\">、</span><a style=\"color: blue; text-decoration: underline;\" href=\"https://rule.jd.com/rule/ruleDetail.action?ruleId=1219901545294991360&amp;type=0&amp;btype=1\"><span style=\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: #4472c4;\">【修订】《京东开放平台医药类目资质标准》</span></a></span></p>\n<p style=\"line-height: 200%; margin-right: 0cm; margin-left: 0cm; font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\"><strong>核心内容：</strong>①删除二级类目&ldquo;挂号&rdquo;资质标准；②调整二级类目&ldquo;在线问诊&rdquo;资质标准；③处方药相关类目新增二级类目名称。</span></p>\n<p style=\"line-height: 200%; margin-right: 0cm; margin-left: 0cm; font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\"><span style=\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: #4472c4;\">2</span><span style=\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: #4472c4;\">、</span><a style=\"color: blue; text-decoration: underline;\" href=\"https://rule.jd.com/rule/ruleDetail.action?ruleId=1211560627345166336\"><span style=\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: #4472c4;\">【修订】《京东开放平台店铺综合体验分规则》</span></a><span style=\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: #4472c4;\"> </span></span></p>\n<p style=\"line-height: 200%; margin-right: 0cm; margin-left: 0cm; font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\"><strong>核心内容：</strong>①物流履约因子项指标调整；②五星店铺认证规则调整。</span></p>\n<p style=\"line-height: 200%; margin-right: 0cm; margin-left: 0cm; font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\"><span style=\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: #4472c4;\">3</span><span style=\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: #4472c4;\">、</span><a style=\"color: blue; text-decoration: underline;\" href=\"https://rule.jd.com/rule/ruleDetail.action?ruleId=1219265844798951424\"><span style=\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: #4472c4;\">【修订】《京东开放平台车厘子/</span><span style=\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: #4472c4;\">樱桃商品管理规则》</span></a><span style=\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: #4472c4;\"> </span></span></p>\n<p style=\"line-height: 200%; margin-right: 0cm; margin-left: 0cm; font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\"><strong>核心内容：</strong>调整等级与分级标准。 </span></p>\n<p style=\"line-height: 200%; margin-right: 0cm; margin-left: 0cm; font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\"><span style=\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: #4472c4;\">4</span><span style=\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: #4472c4;\">、</span><a style=\"color: blue; text-decoration: underline;\" href=\"https://rule.jd.com/rule/ruleDetail.action?ruleId=1220340033161138176\"><span style=\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: #4472c4;\">【修订】《京东开放平台赠品管理规则》</span></a></span></p>\n<p style=\"line-height: 200%; margin-right: 0cm; margin-left: 0cm; font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\"><strong>核心内容：</strong> ①细化不适合作为赠品的类目要求；②主附件、商品说明书等商品自身必备零件不得作为赠品。</span></p>\n<p style=\"line-height: 200%; margin-right: 0cm; margin-left: 0cm; font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\"><span style=\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: #4472c4;\">5</span><span style=\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: #4472c4;\">、</span><a style=\"color: blue; text-decoration: underline;\" href=\"https://rule.jd.com/rule/ruleDetail.action?ruleId=1220321897854668800\"><span style=\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: #4472c4;\">【修订】《京东开放平台资质证据不合格细则》</span></a></span></p>\n<p style=\"line-height: 200%; margin-right: 0cm; margin-left: 0cm; font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\"><strong>核心内容：</strong>新增伪造或提供与事实不符的申诉证据违规定义、处理措施及规则解读。</span></p>\n<p style=\"line-height: 200%; margin-right: 0cm; margin-left: 0cm; font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\"><span style=\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: #4472c4;\">6</span><span style=\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: #4472c4;\">、</span><a style=\"color: blue; text-decoration: underline;\" href=\"https://rule.jd.com/rule/ruleDetail.action?ruleId=1219530565863215104&amp;btype=1\"><span style=\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: #4472c4;\">【修订】《京东开放平台不正当手段获取资源细则》</span></a><span style=\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: #4472c4;\"> </span></span></p>\n<p style=\"line-height: 200%; margin-right: 0cm; margin-left: 0cm; font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\"><strong>核心内容：</strong>调整违约金金额。</span></p>\n<p style=\"line-height: 200%; margin-right: 0cm; margin-left: 0cm; font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\"><span style=\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">关联规则：<span style=\"color: #4472c4;\">【修订】</span></span><a style=\"color: blue; text-decoration: underline;\" href=\"https://rule.jd.com/rule/ruleDetail.action?ruleId=1219533846010269696&amp;btype=12\"><span style=\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: #4472c4;\">《京东开放平台个人/</span><span style=\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: #4472c4;\">个体合规管理规则》</span></a></span></p>\n<p style=\"line-height: 200%; margin-right: 0cm; margin-left: 0cm; font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\"><span style=\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: #4472c4;\">7</span><span style=\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: #4472c4;\">、</span><a style=\"color: blue; text-decoration: underline;\" href=\"https://rule.jd.com/rule/ruleDetail.action?ruleId=1218825172170182656&amp;btype=7\"><span style=\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: #4472c4;\">【新增】《京东开放平台医药商家违规异地发货管理规范》</span></a><span style=\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: #4472c4;\"> </span></span></p>\n<p style=\"line-height: 200%; margin-right: 0cm; margin-left: 0cm; font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\"><strong>核心内容：</strong>要求商家确保发货地址与亮证主体一致，上传与发货地址一致的《药品经营许可证》、《医疗器械经营许可证》、《第二类医疗器械经营备案凭证》等证照。</span></p>\n<p style=\"line-height: 200%; margin-right: 0cm; margin-left: 0cm; font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\"><span style=\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: #4472c4;\">8</span><span style=\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: #4472c4;\">、</span><a style=\"color: blue; text-decoration: underline;\" href=\"https://rule.jd.com/rule/ruleDetail.action?ruleId=1219222110942138368\"><span style=\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: #4472c4;\">【新增】《京东慧采平台管理规则》</span></a><span style=\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: #4472c4;\"> </span></span></p>\n<p style=\"line-height: 200%; margin-right: 0cm; margin-left: 0cm; font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\"><strong>核心内容：</strong>明确报名规范、履约及服务要求、纠纷及违规处理等。</span></p>\n<p style=\"line-height: 200%; margin-right: 0cm; margin-left: 0cm; font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\"><span style=\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: #4472c4;\">9</span><span style=\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: #4472c4;\">、</span><a style=\"color: blue; text-decoration: underline;\" href=\"https://rule.jd.com/rule/ruleDetail.action?ruleId=1220206135827632128\"><span style=\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: #4472c4;\">【新增】《货源平台供货商管理总则》</span></a></span></p>\n<p style=\"line-height: 200%; margin-right: 0cm; margin-left: 0cm; font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\"><strong>核心内容：</strong>明确供货要求、商品管理、发货履约、违规管理等。</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left; line-height: 200%; background: white; margin: 0cm; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size: 16.0pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black; border: none windowtext 1.0pt; padding: 0cm;\">【规则生效】</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; padding: 0px; color: #000000; white-space: normal; text-align: left; line-height: 28px; background-color: white; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 10pt; line-height: 26.6667px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\"><a style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: #666666; text-decoration-line: none;\" href=\"https://rule.jd.com/rule/ruleDetail.action?ruleId=1216939484537556992&amp;btype=1\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0cm; font-size: 12pt; line-height: 32px; color: #4f81bd; border: 1pt none windowtext;\">1</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0cm; font-size: 12pt; line-height: 32px; color: #4f81bd; border: 1pt none windowtext;\">、【新增】《京东开放平台维修保养轮胎类目招商激励政策（2025.3.1-2025.12.31</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0cm; font-size: 12pt; line-height: 32px; color: #4f81bd; border: 1pt none windowtext;\">）</span></a></span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0cm; font-size: 12pt; line-height: 32px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: #4f81bd; border: 1pt none windowtext;\">》</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; padding: 0px; color: #000000; white-space: normal; text-align: left; line-height: 28px; background-color: white; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"left\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0cm; font-size: 12pt; line-height: 32px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black; border: 1pt none windowtext;\">核心内容：</span></strong><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0cm; font-size: 12pt; line-height: 32px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black; border: 1pt none windowtext;\">激励周期内首次入驻并成功启用的店铺，若激励周期内轮胎类目（具体如下表）下的月维度有效销售额&ge;5万元，则直接返还对应类目的2%运营支持服务费至商家京准通账户。</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; padding: 0px; color: #000000; white-space: normal; text-align: left; line-height: 28px; background-color: white; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 12pt; line-height: 32px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\"><a style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: #666666; text-decoration-line: none;\" href=\"https://rule.jd.com/rule/ruleDetail.action?ruleId=1217350212956327936\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0cm; color: #4f81bd; border: 1pt none windowtext;\">2</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0cm; color: #4f81bd; border: 1pt none windowtext;\">、【新增】《京东开放平台宠物猫、宠物狗类目销售激励与考核（2025.1.1-2025.12.31</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0cm; color: #4f81bd; border: 1pt none windowtext;\">）</span></a></span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0cm; font-size: 12pt; line-height: 32px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: #4f81bd; border: 1pt none windowtext;\">》</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; padding: 0px; color: #000000; white-space: normal; text-align: left; line-height: 28px; background-color: white; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"left\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0cm; font-size: 12pt; line-height: 32px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black; border: 1pt none windowtext;\">核心内容：</span></strong><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0cm; font-size: 12pt; line-height: 32px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black; border: 1pt none windowtext;\">每季度第一个月公示上季度商家排名和得分情况，前30%的商家进行现金激励，针对末尾30%的商家进行清退退店处理。</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; padding: 0px; color: #000000; white-space: normal; text-align: left; line-height: 28px; background-color: white; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 12pt; line-height: 32px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\"><a style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: #666666; text-decoration-line: none;\" href=\"https://rule.jd.com/rule/ruleDetail.action?ruleId=1216664781327568896&amp;btype=1\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0cm; color: #4f81bd; border: 1pt none windowtext;\">3</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0cm; color: #4f81bd; border: 1pt none windowtext;\">、【修订】《京东开放平台商品价格管理规则》</span></a></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; padding: 0px; color: #000000; white-space: normal; text-align: left; line-height: 28px; background-color: white; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"left\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0cm; font-size: 12pt; line-height: 32px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black; border: 1pt none windowtext;\">核心内容：</span></strong><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0cm; font-size: 12pt; line-height: 32px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black; background-color: white; border: 1pt none windowtext;\">针对价格违规行为的处理措施项调整，其中&ldquo;要求商家支付10,000元以上1,000,000元以下违约金&rdquo;调整为&ldquo;要求商家支付50元以上1000000元以下违约金&rdquo;。</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; padding: 0px; color: #000000; white-space: normal; text-align: left; line-height: 28px; background-color: white; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 12pt; line-height: 32px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\"><a style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: #666666; text-decoration-line: none;\" href=\"https://rule.jd.com/rule/ruleDetail.action?ruleId=1217423734063894528&amp;btype=6\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0cm; color: #4f81bd; border: 1pt none windowtext;\">4</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0cm; color: #4f81bd; border: 1pt none windowtext;\">、【新增】《京东汽车服务管理规则》</span></a></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; padding: 0px; color: #000000; white-space: normal; text-align: left; line-height: 28px; background-color: white; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"left\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0cm; font-size: 12pt; line-height: 32px; font-family: 微软雅黑, 